{"about_the_game":"<strong>BACK THE KICKSTARTER NOW!</strong><br><br>Art is a young college graduate looking for his first serious job. After a series of unsuccessful interviews, the Grim Reaper itself materializes in front of Art's eyes and, impressed by the young man's skills, offers him a job as an intern at his own company, Death Corp.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146280/extras/Death_Corp_Hood.gif?t=1697002183\" /><br><br>Meet tons of ridiculous characters, harvest the souls of those who recently passed away and, sometimes, push forward fate by solving outrageous and hilarious puzzles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146280/extras/DEATH_CORP_Game_JASON.gif?t=1697002183\" /><br><br>Dark humor with bright colors scenes divided in independent chapters with constant references to film and book genres, pop culture and classic point and click games.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146280/extras/Death-Corp-Seagul.gif?t=1697002183\" /><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic 2D point-and-click adventure (just the way you like it!)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A wicked story full of fantasy and humor</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hand-drawn backgrounds, characters, and interface!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mixed of frame by frame and squeleton animations</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play the Demo now!</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146280/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1697002183","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146280/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1697002183","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146280/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1697002183","capsule_imagev5":"https://